description:

All of my works is free. If you'd like to support me, feel free to buy me a coffee. 👍

With LoRA, you can generate big boob suzuka! :D

Recommend options

    • Casual clothes :

      • hair flower, black pantyhose, pleated skirt, blue skirt, white shirt, short sleeves

    • Alternate costume:

      • Suzuka has NO official alternate clothes. :(

  • Use animefull based model

    • DPM++ Series(SDE Karras, 2M Karras, etc.)

    • about 20 steps, CFG scale 3.5~6.5

    • kl-f8-anime2.vae

    • CLIP skip = 1

    • If using highres

      • Latent series

      • Denoising strength 0.50~0.65

LoRA training info

  • based on Animefull-pruned

  • 226 images of silence suzuka

    • 4x low quality 80 images

    • 8x medium quality 71 images

    • 16x high quality 75 images

    • => 1 epoch = 2088 images

  • replaced character feature tags with silence suzuka \(umamusume\)

    • horse girl, horse tail, orange hair, blue eyes, etc.

  • using aspect ratio bucketing

  • resolution : 768x768

  • rank=alpha=16

  • using dadaptation

  • batch size = 4, 7 epochs trained

  • clip skip = 1

This LoRA may be compatible with animefull-based models (ex. AbyssOrangeMix Series...)

All uploaded images are generated by AOM3A1
